  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Scout-Nin Keyword: Tactical</p><p>When you would make an attack or cast a jutsu that would deal damage to a creature their reactionary attempts were already a part of your calculations. </p><p>Spend one superiority die, recording the result. </p><p>If the target would reduce your damage or gain temporary hit points as a result of a Reaction based jutsu, feature or trait, you reduce their damage reduction or temporary hit point value by an amount equal to twice the result of your superiority die until the end of the current turn.</p>",
